ygData.messageBody:
Hail!

Iceiallana the first was a 54 Druid on Brell. She rescued a Highalander who
was lost in the fairy world and he named his first and only daughter after her
:-) She has chosen to study the healing arts and sneaks into the basement of
the Acadamy where Merlin's old scrolls are hidden to learn more of the
Goddess. She is now in Avalon Marshes researching her mother's religious
affiliations and will become a priestess of both her God and the Goddess
which, in all likelihood, will have her branded a heretic somewhere down the
lines.

*giggles* Nice to be playing again :-)

Ice
